WEBVTT


00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:02.380
I don't care what anybody says,

00:00:02.400 --> 00:00:05.880
if you hear a man saying that he hates Taylor Swift,

00:00:05.881 --> 00:00:10.441
what he's really saying is that he hates all women.

00:00:10.442 --> 00:00:11.041
Okay, great.

00:00:11.042 --> 00:00:12.741
Now that I've got everyone's attention.

00:00:12.880 --> 00:00:15.620
Um, thank you so much.

00:00:15.800 --> 00:00:18.660
Look at this. We are almost there.

00:00:19.160 --> 00:00:22.640
Only 8,000, less than 8,000 euros to go.

00:00:22.641 --> 00:00:25.141
A couple days ago, this was at 15.

00:00:25.680 --> 00:00:28.360
So, thank you so much for donating to this.

00:00:28.361 --> 00:00:33.941
It is amazing. 1,386 people have donated.

00:00:34.160 --> 00:00:36.700
Abdul and his family are living in ruins.

00:00:36.960 --> 00:00:39.000
They simply don't have a choice.

00:00:39.001 --> 00:00:43.641
Their home was bombed. It's really hard to provide food for your family

00:00:43.642 --> 00:00:47.121
when a bag of flour costs $1,000.

00:00:47.122 --> 00:00:49.421
Imagine going down to the supermarket

00:00:49.520 --> 00:00:53.460
and having to spend $1,000 on a bag of flour.

00:00:53.560 --> 00:00:56.880
So, coordinating an exit cost 5,000.

00:00:56.881 --> 00:00:58.761
So, with this money,

00:00:58.762 --> 00:01:03.301
we're going to be able to evacuate three families,

00:01:03.560 --> 00:01:05.880
15 people. When you donate,

00:01:05.881 --> 00:01:07.561
you go and click on the link

00:01:07.562 --> 00:01:10.161
and you can literally donate with Apple Pay.

00:01:10.162 --> 00:01:12.781
So, it is literally just a click of the button.

00:01:13.080 --> 00:01:15.040
It does not take any time.

00:01:15.041 --> 00:01:16.841
It literally takes under 30 seconds.

00:01:16.842 --> 00:01:21.321
And I just, I don't understand why the billionaires on doing it,

00:01:21.322 --> 00:01:23.121
but they're not. So,

00:01:23.122 --> 00:01:26.041
if you do have any money, please do that.

00:01:26.042 --> 00:01:30.073
If you can share it, please share it. Please. Thank you.
